Package: spinifex
Title: Manual Tours, Manual Control of the Contribution a Single Variable make to a Projection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicholas", "Spyrison", email = "spyrison@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dianne", "Cook", role = c("aut", "ths"))
    )
Description: Generates the path for Manual Tours. Tours are dynamic orthogonal 
  linear projections of numeric multivariate data (p>3). Implements manual 
  tours, for manual of crotrol of the contributions of the selected variable 
  with the projection space. Additionally allows other tours to be rendered 
  using the gganimate and plotly animation packages.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0),
    tourr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
